Direct Known Subclasses:
KMedoidsSupervised
public class KMedoids
extends weka.clusterers.RandomizableClusterer
implements weka.clusterers.NumberOfClustersRequestable, weka.core.WeightedInstancesHandler, java.io.Serializable

Cluster data using the kMedoids algorithm.

Valid options are: 

 -N <num>
  number of clusters.
  (default 2).
 -A <classname and options>
  Distance function to use.
 
 -I <num>
  Maximum number of iterations.
 
 -O
  Preserve order of instances.
